You are a senior product engineer + UX designer. Build a production-ready marketing website for an AI product company called “NeuronFish” from scratch.


## GOAL
Create a modern, fast, SEO-friendly website for NeuronFish (Bangladesh) using:
- Next.js (latest) with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- ESLint configured
- Clean component structure
- Accessible UI (WCAG-friendly)
- Great mobile responsiveness
- Simple but premium look


NeuronFish builds AI-powered products.

Products:
1) DIKKHA (D-I-K-K-H-A) — Educational AI-powered app for Bangladeshi students (Class 9 & 10)
2) CHHAR — Location-based discounts/promotions app for Bangladesh; currently focused on Dhaka
We recently bought our main company domain and want a professional site that looks like a real startup.


