## SITE-WIDE REQUIREMENTS
- Sticky responsive navbar with links: Home, Products, About, Blog (optional), Contact
- Mobile nav with hamburger + slide-down menu
- Footer with sitemap, product links, contact, socials
- SEO:
  - Per-page metadata (title/description)
  - OpenGraph defaults
  - Basic robots.txt + sitemap generation
- Performance:
  - Use next/image
  - Avoid heavy libraries
- Accessibility:
  - Semantic headings
  - Focus states
  - Proper labels + aria attributes in forms


## TECH REQUIREMENTS
- Tailwind-based mini design system:
  - Reusable components: Button, Container, SectionHeading, Card, Badge, FeatureList, CTA, FAQAccordion, TeamCard, Avatar, Toast
- Consistent layout:
  - app/layout.tsx with global styles
  - Optional route group app/(site)/...
- Keep dependencies minimal; acceptable:
  - lucide-react for icons
  - class-variance-authority (optional)
  - @tailwindcss/typography (optional for blog)
## CONTENT REQUIREMENTS
- Polished English copy
- Bangladesh-relevant, mention Dhaka for CHHAR
- Keep claims realistic; do not invent awards/partners
- Use local placeholder images in /public (simple gradients/mock cards are fine)
