## IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS
- Create the project structure as if running:
  - npx create-next-app@latest neuronfish-web --ts --tailwind --eslint --app
- Then add all pages, components, and styles.
- Add environment variable patterns for future email provider:
  - RESEND_API_KEY, CONTACT_TO_EMAIL, etc.
- Contact form behavior:
  - If env vars missing, fallback to console logging and still show success UI.
